Third-party notices for toard-shim
==================================

ccusage
-------
The following files contain code derived from ccusage
(https://github.com/ryoppippi/ccusage), commit
cdda1821cf8a130c4d92cfd5aec101dfba96e1c9, licensed under the MIT License:

  - shim/rust/src/collect/gemini.rs
      derived from rust/crates/ccusage/src/adapter/gemini/{parser,paths,loader}.rs
  - shim/rust/src/collect/qwen.rs
      derived from rust/crates/ccusage/src/adapter/qwen/{parser,paths}.rs
  - shim/rust/src/collect/gemini_family.rs
      derived from rust/crates/ccusage/src/adapter/jsonl.rs and src/utils.rs

Modifications from upstream: cost calculation (PricingMap), report
aggregation, and parallel file reading were removed; parsed records are
mapped to toard's RawUsage (reasoning/thoughts tokens are folded into
output_tokens, matching upstream's billable usage).

